'''Halmad Prime''' was a well-reputed [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage from [[Halmad/Legends|Halmad]]. It was only available for export, not on-[[Planet/Legends|planet]]. It was most often available through [[Black market/Legends|black market]] deals.

==Behind the scenes==
The production of luxury goods for export only mirrors the [[Wikipedia:Free trade zone|free trade zones]] in developing nations on Earth such as the [[Wikipedia:Dominican Republic|Dominican Republic]], which produce products like [[Wikipedia:Cigar|cigars]] and [[Wikipedia:Rum|rum]] for the world market that are not allowed to be sold locally.

